title.narrative: Global Health Supply Chain Program -Business Intelligence & Analytics (GHSC-BI&A)

description.narrative: This contract will serve as a primary vehicle through which USAID can house program data, perform analysis and understand data trends in support of global health programs. To accomplish this overall contract goal, IntelliCog will: Provide a software as a service data collection and analysis solution; establish a web-based data warehouse; create analysis, graphics, and dashboards around data sets; integrate data sets to allow for cross-data comparisons; promote data governance policies and processes; provide data analyst support to help data owners understand and create meaningful data analysis; and collaborate with global partners (e.g. Global Fund, UNFPA, etc.) and other contractors within the Global Health Supply Chain Program to allow data exchange and analysis.
